00:17:59.180 --> 00:18:05.180
All right, so this is the server part of the, this is the server part code for that application.

00:18:05.180 --> 00:18:08.180
It's not too complicated.

00:18:08.180 --> 00:18:12.180
These are the important parts.

00:18:12.180 --> 00:18:17.180
So first, there's this reactive values that stores sum.

00:18:17.780 --> 00:18:24.780
I've got an observe event, which every time the add button is clicked, it adds the current

00:18:24.780 --> 00:18:27.780
value of input n to the sum.

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:39.780
And then, and then when val set sum changes, that causes this render text to be triggered

