when you say enable bookmarking.

00:28:33.380 --> 00:28:35.380
What you need to do

00:28:35.979 --> 00:28:37.979
is use the onBookmark

00:28:37.979 --> 00:28:39.979
callback function

00:28:39.979 --> 00:28:41.979
extract that file content

00:28:41.979 --> 00:28:43.979
and then save it in state$values$

00:28:43.979 --> 00:28:45.979
file content

00:28:45.979 --> 00:28:47.979
and then with the onRestore

00:28:47.979 --> 00:28:49.979
then you'd restore it there.

